23/03/2006
ANKARA, Turkey -- Army chief General Hilmi Ozkok opened a two-day international anti-terror forum in Ankara Thursday (23 March) saying all nations must unite against terrorism.
Senior military and political representatives from various states are attending the conference, including Afghan President Hamid Karzai.
(Focus, CNN Turk - 23/03/06;
NTV, TurkishPress.com - 22/03/06)
